    <item>
      <title>尽管工资成本影响利润，维斯塔斯风机销量仍大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/vestas-signals-jump-in-wind-turbine-orders-after-profit-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维斯塔斯风力发电系统公司 (Vestas Wind Systems A/S) 试图安抚投资者，该公司报告称风力涡轮机订单激增，而两天前该公司还发布了与其不同业务部分相关的盈利预警。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/vestas-signals-jump-in-wind-turbine-orders-after-profit-warning</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 06:20:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡元在政策收紧观点的推动下升至 18 个月高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/sgd-usd-singapore-dollar-advances-toward-18-month-high-on-rate-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场预测新加坡央行今年将采取相对美联储更为紧缩的货币政策，新加坡元兑美元延续涨势，升至 18 个月高点，这对新加坡元有利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/sgd-usd-singapore-dollar-advances-toward-18-month-high-on-rate-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 04:18:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
